{{Italic title}}
'''''Informal Logic''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] academic journal that deals with multi-disciplinary topics related to [[reasoning]] and [[argumentation]]; covering both theory and practice. Topics covered include, but are not limited to, philosophy, rhetoric, communication, linguistics, psychology, and  law.

